title: Arbor Snowboards :: Welcome To Arbor - Mark Carter
description:
Welcome to Arbor, Mark.
The power of Mark’s snowboarding abilities is only multiplied by the duality of his character. Few riders posses the work ethic, charismatic personality, and on snow skills that Carter personifies. Having Carter on the team adds a new level of energy and fortitude to Arbor as we move into our 20th year of production.
